ss.getName());\n\n        assertThat(resource).isNotNull();\n        assertThat(resource.toExternalForm()).endsWith(\"/javassist/ClassClassPath.class\");\n    }\n}\n"}], "isError": false, "timestamp": 1777408565445}]}
